high_descs: Exit the room and turn left to enter the bedroom on the right to reach the dresser next to the sidetable next to the bed.
Pick up the butterknife from the dresser.
Turn around to exit the room on the left and head to the bedroom on the right to reach the apple.
Cut the apple on the dresser with the knife.
Turn left to exit the room and head to the room on the right across the passage to reach the round coffeetable.
Put the butterknife on the coffeetable.
Turn around to exit the room and head to the bedroom across the passage to reach the dresser.
Pick up a slice of the apple from the dresser.
Turn left to exit the room and turn left to enter the kitchen on the right to reach the fridge.
Cool the slice of apple in the fridge and take the apple out.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Put the slice of apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled slice of Apple in the Microwave.

Place the butterknife on the left corner of the coffeetable.

Pick up a slice of the apple from the right front side.
Turn left at the door and go across to the fridge.
Place the apple in the fridge, then pick the apple back up.
Turn around to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
